Prototype Description: Subjective feelings such as fatigue, weakness, or exhaustion
Difficulty performing physical activities or exercise, reduced tolerance
Difficulty breathing or feeling unable to get enough air
Signs related to blood, bleeding disorders, or bruising
Symptoms related to metabolic imbalances like diabetes, thirst, urination, sugar irregularities
Changes in vision such as blurring or distortion
Changes in body weight or hunger patterns
Restlessness, lethargy, altered mental or behavioral state
